第三是尋找合適你的個人輔導

00:02:05.666 --> 00:02:07.524
Now the first. Going back to the first
首先回到家庭治療，

00:02:07.524 --> 00:02:08.849
Seeking family therapy.
首先回到家庭治療，

00:02:08.849 --> 00:02:10.856
Why would I recommend that?
我為什麼這樣建議?

00:02:10.856 --> 00:02:13.703
I would recommend family therapy to people because it gives you
這是因家庭治療能讓你們

