而在處理家庭和抑鬱症有經驗的治療師

00:02:43.901 --> 00:02:45.624
It would be a great experience for all of you
能有地方安心地抒發

00:02:45.637 --> 00:02:49.146
and a safe place to vent about what's going on in your family.
家庭正經歷的事情會是一種很好的經驗。

00:02:49.146 --> 00:02:52.335
Now the second thing. Externalising the problem
現在到第二步，把問題外化

00:02:52.335 --> 00:02:55.379
I know this sounds silly, but it can really really help the person
我想聽起來有點怪，但這做法

00:02:55.379 --> 00:02:58.088
