把問題外化是指，不要說

00:03:02.196 --> 00:03:03.727
"You made me feel this way" or
”你令我感到這樣” 或是

00:03:03.727 --> 00:03:04.997
"When you did that,
”當你這樣做，

00:03:04.997 --> 00:03:07.446
I felt terrible and that was really hurtful".
我的感覺很差、覺真的很受傷害”

00:03:07.446 --> 00:03:10.756
Instead of having those kinds of arguments/conversations,
不要作出爭辯，

00:03:10.756 --> 00:03:12.939
it can really help to say, "You know,
可以說”你知道嗎，

